<BaseLayout title="Zero Knowledge Proofs" crumb="Introduction">
  <article class="intro-page">
    <div class="overview">

      <div class="overview-eyebrow">A Cryptography Guide</div>

      <h1 class="overview-title">Zero Knowledge<br>Proofs</h1>

      <p class="overview-desc">
        The cryptographic primitive that lets you prove knowledge of a secret
        without ever revealing it. Covers theory, protocols, zkSNARKs, zkSTARKs,
        and real-world applications.
      </p>

